Oasis-Infobyte Projects
1. Landing Page Website
Project Overview

This is a responsive landing page for a fictional institution. The page includes a navigation bar, a carousel, a welcome section, a notice board, and various other sections like Programs, Admissions, Testimonials, Events, and Contact Information.
Features

    Responsive Design: Optimized for both desktop and mobile devices.
    Carousel: Slideshow feature to showcase important images.
    Dynamic Content: Includes various sections to display important information such as notices and upcoming events.
    Stylish Buttons and Links: CSS-styled buttons and links for an enhanced user experience.

Technologies Used

    HTML5
    CSS3
    Bootstrap 4
    JavaScript

Usage

Clone this repository and open index.html in your browser to view the landing page.
2. Portfolio Website
Project Overview

This portfolio website showcases the projects and skills of an individual. It includes sections such as About, Skills, Projects, and Contact. The site is designed to be a professional and clean presentation of your work.
Features

    Personal Information Section: Displays your name, profession, and a brief bio.
    Skills Section: Lists your technical skills and proficiencies.
    Projects Showcase: Highlights your completed projects with descriptions and links.
    Contact Form: Allows visitors to send you messages directly from the website.

Technologies Used

    HTML5
    CSS3
    JavaScript

Usage

Clone this repository and open portfolio.html in your browser to view the portfolio website.
3. Temperature Converter
Project Overview

This is a simple temperature converter application that allows users to convert temperatures between Celsius, Fahrenheit, and Kelvin. The application is designed to be user-friendly and provides instant conversion results.
Features

    Celsius to Fahrenheit/Kelvin Conversion
    Fahrenheit to Celsius/Kelvin Conversion
    Kelvin to Celsius/Fahrenheit Conversion

Technologies Used

    HTML5
    CSS3
    JavaScript

Usage

Clone this repository and open temp_converter.html in your browser to use the temperature converter.
Repository

All the projects are available in this repository: Oasis-Infobyte.
